  "body": "# Problem\r\nCurrently due to technical limitations sync devices flow is working only when both devices are in the same network and VPN also may affect the ability to finish the flow successfully.\r\nSo it has to be explicit for the user that they must use the same WI-FI network with a stable connection.\r\n\r\nIn the current mobile [design](https://www.figma.com/file/o4qG1bnFyuyFOvHQVGgeFY/Onboarding-for-Mobile?node-id=4121-312366&t=cu0LmMROIe8dnyuF-4) it is not anticipated.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\nThe user is warned that both devices have to be in the same network and not use VPN services \r\n\r\ncc @John-44 @pedro-et \r\n",
